(ii) Shall also be applicable to those cases in which the defendant
elects to waive the defendant’s right to trial and pay the fine or penalty deposit established
by the Chief Judge of the District Court by administrative regulation.
(f) (1) This subsection does not apply to a traffic case under § 21–202.1,
